name: Bullet Hell (34545Allan)
description:
A simple bullet hell created for Godot Game Jam 3

Known Issues:

- Cannot collect junk while in damaged animation

- Sometimes take double damage if two instances of damage are very close together

- Second enemy type doesn't always play explosion animation on destruction

- SFX + Rotation continue occuring on enemy type 3 during explosion animation
